WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.800 --> 00:00:04.633
It’s been half an hour.

2
00:00:04.666 --> 00:00:07.166
The Emperor immediately put me under the covers when he arrived.

3
00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:09.966
He’s been dealing with court documents by himself for half an hour.

4
00:00:13.400 --> 00:00:14.233
Your Majesty.

5
00:00:16.300 --> 00:00:17.466
Why aren’t you asleep yet?

6
00:00:17.466 --> 00:00:21.166
Your Majesty, I haven’t even gone through the formal ceremony yet.

7
00:00:21.300 --> 00:00:22.966
Is it appropriate to be in the Yangxin Hall like this?

8
00:00:23.200 --> 00:00:24.333
Don’t worry, I won’t touch you.

9
00:00:24.333 --> 00:00:26.300
Who cares whether you touch me or not?

10
00:00:26.333 --> 00:00:28.600
What I care about is my own reputation.

11
00:00:28.600 --> 00:00:30.966
Your Majesty.

12
00:00:32.133 --> 00:00:33.000
If this matter gets out,

13
00:00:33.066 --> 00:00:36.633
the officials will damage Your Majesty’s reputation.

14
00:00:36.933 --> 00:00:39.000
My Empress is still so concerned about me.

15
00:00:39.766 --> 00:00:42.300
Don’t worry, they won’t dare to gossip.

16
00:00:44.300 --> 00:00:46.633
I hope so.

17
00:00:47.533 --> 00:00:49.700
In my past life, your favoring Consort Yan

18
00:00:49.900 --> 00:00:52.100
almost got drowned in the spittle of the officials.

19
00:00:52.100 --> 00:00:55.000
I understand now.

20
00:00:01.466 --> 00:01:03.000
The Emperor is definitely using me to silence those officials.

21
00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:03.700
Dog Emperor.

22
00:01:03.700 --> 00:01:06.300
He’s deliberately neglecting Consort Yan

23
00:01:06.400 --> 00:01:08.133
and creating a false impression of favoring me.

24
00:01:08.133 --> 00:01:10.500
He wants me to attract the officials’ anger.

25
00:01:10.533 --> 00:01:12.366
His beloved consort suffers a temporary grievance,

26
00:01:14.800 --> 00:01:17.766
while I will become the thorn in the officials’ side.

27
00:01:17.766 --> 00:01:21.033
A thorn in the flesh.

28
00:01:21.166 --> 00:01:22.400
What sin have I committed in this world?

29
00:01:29.733 --> 00:01:32.166
Why must I serve this dog Emperor

30
00:01:32.400 --> 00:01:34.300
as a beast of burden in both lives?

31
00:01:34.300 --> 00:01:35.466
Why?

32
00:02:01.566 --> 00:02:03.966
I can feel you’re intentionally delaying.

33
00:02:04.766 --> 00:02:05.833
Actually,

34
00:02:06.533 --> 00:02:09.266
I understand that you don’t want to come to the palace.

35
00:02:11.166 --> 00:02:13.466
But I insist.

36
00:02:14.366 --> 00:02:15.566
My Empress

37
00:02:15.800 --> 00:02:17.100
must be you.
